          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "O Lord, how many are Your works! In wisdom You have made them all; The earth is full of Your possessions. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "O Lord, how many are Your works! In wisdom You have made them all; The earth is full of Your possessions."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "O Lord, how many are Your works! In wisdom You have made them all; The earth is full of Your possessions."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "There is the sea, great and broad, In which are swarms without number, Animals both small and great. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "There is the sea, great and broad, In which are swarms without number, Animals both small and great."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "There is the sea, great and broad, In which are swarms without number, Animals both small and great."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
